    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "Only those most worthy and devoted servants of the Storm Lord are granted these powerful holy symbols.\n\nTalos is the destructive force of nature. He is the god of storms, forest fires, earthquakes, tornadoes, and general destruction.  He attracts the destroyer, the raider, the looter, and the brigand among his followers.\n\nTalos the Destroyer is the dark side of nature, the uncaring and destructive force that lies waiting to strike at any time. Talos is more feared than worshipped, which seems to account for his great popularity as much as anything. "
